<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>LIVING WATER</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zietak ahin hintui a luong,
 Kalvari-a hung pawt chuh;
 Mi tamtak hihdam na'n a luong,
 Kuole a dawn nuom cheng chuh;
 Nang, Eden natna vei zing khan,
 Hung inla va dawn meng in;
 Chun Kalvari tui chimtak kha,
 Na lunggil ah luong ina.

[V2]
 2. Chun, zie tui hi hezing inla,
 Mi dang le hun hetsak in;
 Mi kuole zie tui dawn ta chuh,
 Dam tei tei ina, ti'n la-
 Isu lopina hung hina,
 Van Angel thiengtho te khun;
 Kipah la kiko pih unau,
 I pau Pathien ma a khun.

[V3]
 3. Zie apat hin kumsawt chanin,
 Zie hinna tui hi a luong;
 Thokit chaten a tui thiengtho,
 Kumkhaw sawtin dawn ta'n au;
 Belam No hinna thiengtho in,
 Hukdamte kivak un au;
 Eden thillui um talo in,
 Hin thakin leng zing ta'n au.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>351</hymn_number>
</song>